      Sinnamon Park was designed from the ground up as a family suburb, and the estate planning shows in how it has held up over time. Consistent housing quality, integrated parklands and Centenary Motorway access make this one of the western corridor's most dependable family addresses.
    </p>
<!-- APPRAISAL FORM -->
<div style="background:#fff; border-left:4px solid #b98229; padding:2rem 2rem 1.75rem; margin:2rem 0; border-radius:16px;">
