<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I know Sinnamon Park well. The estate's consistent housing quality and low stock turnover mean that when quality homes do come to market, motivated buyers are already waiting.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Sinnamon Park's street layout, integrated parklands and consistent housing quality give the suburb a uniformity that makes buyers comfortable and reduces valuation risk. Centenary Motorway access puts the CBD within about 20 minutes drive, and Indooroopilly Shopping Centre is five kilometres north for major retail. The suburb consistently attracts young families upgrading from further west, and the relatively low turnover of quality homes means well-presented properties draw genuine competition when they come to market. Park-fronting positions and corner blocks are the strongest addresses within the estate, and they consistently achieve premiums over comparably sized internal lots.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Western Brisbane</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">13km from CBD</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Family Friendly</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Planned estate lifestyle</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/indooroopilly" style="color:#b98229;">Indooroopilly</a>, <a href="/suburbs/kenmore" style="color:#b98229;">Kenmore</a>, <a href="/suburbs/jindalee" style="color:#b98229;">Jindalee</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

